   - Changed from `std::unordered_map` to thread-local `CompactHashTable`
   - Pre-sized based on expected cardinality (2M groups / num_threads)
   - Merge phase combines thread-local tables with proper value accumulation
   - All [TIMING] lines preserved inside #ifdef guards
   - All encoding logic unchanged

